# Hookbase webhook handler — Cloudflare Worker + {{PROVIDER_LABEL}}

```bash
npm install
cp .dev.vars.example .dev.vars
# edit .dev.vars with your signing secret
npx wrangler dev
```

POSTs land at `/webhook`. Signature verification uses Web Crypto — no Node modules required.

## Deploying

```bash
npx wrangler secret put {{ENV_VAR_NAME}}
npx wrangler deploy
```
